(2, 1, '2017-11-07 05:19:18', '2017-11-07 05:19:18', '<div class=\"content-block pl-10\">\r\n<div class=\"section-title\">\r\n<h2 class=\"title\">О Компании</h2>\r\n</div>\r\nArt Building Group - одна из ведущих строительных компаний Узбекистана с 10-летним опытом работы в сфере строительства жилых и нежилых комплексов. Компания основана в 2004 году и объединяет такие предприятия как Art Mega Bulding и Art Building Plus. География деятельности Art Building Group - Ташкент, Самарканд, Сурхандарья и другие.\r\n<div class=\"row mt-30\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div class=\"feature-box left_bor left_pos ex-small\">\r\n<p><i class=\"glyph-icon flaticon-construction-26\"></i></p>\r\n<h3 class=\"title\">Гарантируем надежность</h3>\r\nНа выполненные работы и поставленные материалы действуют гарантии качества\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div class=\"feature-box left_bor left_pos ex-small\"><i class=\"glyph-icon flaticon-projection-screen-with-bar-chart\"></i>\r\n<h3 class=\"title\">Работаем <br> комплексно</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\nArt Building Group может обеспечить реализацию всех этапов проекта\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Главная', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'home', '', '', '2017-12-18 13:58:47', '2017-12-18 13:58:47', '', 0, 'http://artbuilding.uz/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(4, 1, '2017-11-07 05:24:07', '2017-11-07 05:24:07', 'This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\r\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\r\n...or something like this:\r\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Sample Page', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-11-07 05:24:07', '2017-11-07 05:24:07', '', 2, 'http://artbuilding.uz/2017/11/07/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
