(300, 1, '2017-12-15 07:37:18', '2017-12-15 07:37:18', 'An agreement on the construction of a new cement plant in the republic, which will be the largest in Central Asia, was concluded within the framework of the visit to Uzbekistan of Russian Prime Minister Dmitry Medvedev.\r\nThe agreement on the project was signed by the chairman of the board of directors of Eurocement, Filaret Galchev, and the chairman of the board of Uzstroymaterialy, Botir Zaripov. The contractor is Beijing Triumph International Engineering Co. (part of the industrial group CNBM, PRC), stated in a press release, \"Eurocement Group.\"\r\nThe contract requires the contractor to carry out design, construction, supply, fabrication and installation of equipment, as well as training of personnel. The project will be implemented by 2020. The plant will be equipped with high-tech equipment.\r\nAs noted in the press materials, the need for a new plant is due to the fact that the capacity of Akhangarancement is now 100% loaded, and the demand for the company\'s products is increasing not only in Uzbekistan but also in neighboring countries.', 'Eurocement will invest $ 160 million in the construction of a cement plant in Uzbekistan', 'Eurocement will invest more than $ 160 million in the construction of a cement plant in the Tashkent region of Uzbekistan on the basis of the Akhangarancement plant, a \"dry process\".', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'eurocement-will-invest-160-million-in-the-construction-of-a-cement-plant-in-uzbekistan-2', '', '', '2017-12-15 07:37:18', '2017-12-15 07:37:18', '', 0, 'http://artbuilding.uz/?post_type=news&#038;p=300', 0, 'news', '', 0),
(301, 1, '2017-12-15 07:53:07', '2017-12-15 07:53:07', '<div class=\"col-lg-9 col-md-9\">\r\n<div class=\"service-block\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12\">\r\n<h4 class=\"mb-20\">Supply of Mahadev Marmo materials</h4>\r\n<p class=\"mb-30\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Art Building Group supplies marble, granite and onyx from Mahadev Marmo Pvl Ltd from the best deposits in India to construction sites in Tashkent and regions of Uzbekistan at favorable prices. \r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mb-20\"><img class=\"img-responsive center-block\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/file-2-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6\">\r\nFor our clients we can offer:\r\n<ul class=\"list-mark\">\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Special prices and optimal terms of delivery;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Delivery of any volume of necessary building and finishing material to the object;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Facing, finishing and installation works of any complexity;</li> 	\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Guarantee the quality of work and the provision of a certificate;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Help in the selection of marble and granite for projects.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 mt-20\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Delivery of marble, granite and onyx from the company Art Building Group</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-20\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">An important advantage of the Art Building Group is the prompt delivery of any volumes of natural material. Stones are supplied in slabs, blocks, slabs and products. The format and processing of the delivered slabs is determined in accordance with the required dimensions for a particular project, in accordance with the specifications. The specifications are transferred by the Customer or ar