(328, 1, '2017-12-15 13:46:24', '2017-12-15 13:46:24', '<div class=\"col-lg-9 col-md-9\">\r\n<div class=\"service-block\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12\">\r\n<h4 class=\"mb-20\">Prefabricated buildings</h4>\r\n<p class=\"mb-30\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Prefabricated buildings are a modern solution in the construction market. They are built in a short time, have excellent characteristics, are affordable. The construction process is as simple as possible and does not require the involvement of a large number of workers and special equipment. Art Building Group offers you the following services:</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mb-20\"><img class=\"img-responsive center-block\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/021.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6\">\r\n<ul class=\"list-mark\">\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">warehouses, hangars;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">shopping facilities (covered markets, shops, shopping malls);</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">industrial buildings (shops, workshops, etc.);</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">car-care centers and car dealerships;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">social, administrative, office buildings;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">sports objects;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">residential buildings and hotels.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 mt-20\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Prefabricated buildings of sandwich panels from the company Art Building Group</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-20\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Group of companies Art Building Group is engaged in the construction of prefabricated buildings of sandwich panels and offers you the following:\r\nBearing structure - metal or wooden frame. Metal frames are assembled from profiles of different sections. Profiles are made of galvanized steel or steel with an anticorrosive polymer coating. To protect against the appearance of cold bridges, perforated thermoprofiles are used.\r\nWalling. The best solution is a sandwich panel. Such panels consist of several layers. The outer layer is a profiled sheet, protected from corrosion by galvanizing and applying a polymer coating. The inner layer is OSB, fiberboard, gypsum board, chipboard and other materials. The middle layer is a heater (expanded polystyrene, mineral wool, etc.). The color of the outer layer forms the appearance of the facades. The inner layer is used for finishing. Such enclosing structures are durable, energy-efficient and reliable.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Why choose our company?</h5>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box left_pos small mt-30\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex;height:36px\">\r\n<img src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/house.svg\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\">\r\n<span>Attractive appearance</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Prefabricated buildings look neat and modern.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box left_pos small mt-30\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex;height:36px\">\r\n<img src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/drawing.svg\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\">\r\n<span>Excellent performance</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sandwich panels are environmentally safe and fireproof.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box left_pos small mt-30\">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex;height:36px\">\r\n<img src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/time-is-money.svg\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\">\r\n<span>Advantageous price and deadline</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Premises are erected by a frame method from prefabricated panels and reduces the cost of using the equipment.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\r\n<h5>Our advantage</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-30\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Our company uses high-quality materials, guarantees correct installation, offers a large selection of prefabricated buildings.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"list-mark\">\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">buildings resistant to weather conditions;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">the structures have the correct geometry;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">selection of the optimal technological solution;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">fast transportation and unloading of materials;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">simple and reliable installation in a short time;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">long service life;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">environmental and fire safety;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">use of certified materials.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In the construction company Art Building Group you can order a full range of works: preparation of the territory for construction and selection of a prefabricated building, its design and installation, connection of communications and interior decoration. We work quickly, competently and with a guarantee of quality.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Prefabricated buildings', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'prefabricated-buildings', '', '', '2017-12-27 15:37:20', '2017-12-27 15:37:20', '', 0, 'http://artbuilding.uz/?post_type=services&#038;p=328', 0, 'services', '', 0),
