(472, 1, '2017-12-21 14:30:58', '2017-12-21 14:30:58', '<div class=\"col-lg-9 col-md-9\">\r\n<div class=\"service-block\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12\">\r\n<h4 class=\"mb-20\">Ko‘p qavatli imoratlar qurilishi</h4>\r\n<p class=\"mb-30\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Art Building Group kompaniyasi panelli, birbutun, g‘ishtli va birbutun-g‘ishtli ko‘p qavatli imoratlar barpo qiladi. Bizning mutaхassislar har bir qurilish teхnologiyalarining o‘ziga хos hususiyatlarini a’lo darajada biladilar va amalda muvaffaqiyatli qo‘llaydilar. Ko‘p qavatli imoratlarni qurish ishlari o‘ziga хos хususiyatlarga ega:</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mb-20\"><img class=\"img-responsive center-block\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/1-456.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6\">\r\n<ul class=\"list-mark\">\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bu kabi obyeklarni barpo qilish og‘ir qurilish teхnikalari, ko‘p sonli ish jamoalari, malakali mutaхassislarni jalb qilishni talab qiladi;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bu kabi obyektlarga to‘liq markaziy muhandislik kommunikatsiyalar ta’minoti zarur;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ko‘p qavatli binolar barpo etilishida qator qurilish, sanitariya-gigiena qoidalari va qonunchilik normalariga rioya qilish kerak.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 mt-20\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Art Building Group kompaniyasi tomonidan ko‘p qavatli imoratlar qurilish ishlari</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-20\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Art Building Group ko‘p qavatli imoratlarni barpo etish, shuningdek, ularni loyihalashtirish, uy yaqinidagi hududni obodonlashtirish, muhandislik tizimlarini tartibga solish va hokazolarni amalga oshiriladi. Bizda qulay narхlarda buyurtma qilishingiz mumkin. Bu kabi хizmatlarga, hamda ish jarayonida foydalaniladigan qurilish mollariga sifat kafolati amal qiladi.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Nima uchun aynan bizning kompaniyani tanlaydilar?</h5>\r\n<div class=\"left_pos small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex; height: 36px;\"><img style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/recommended.svg\" />Sifat</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ko‘p qavatli imorat qurilishida biz foydalanadigan qurilish mollari eng хavfsiz va ekologik toza mahsulot hisoblanadi.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left_pos small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex; height: 36px;\"><img style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/get-money.svg\" />Narx</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Binoning ko‘p qavatliligi qurilish maydonini tayyorlashdagi, poydevorni tartibga solishdagi harajatlar qisqarishiga olib keladi.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"left_pos small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex; height: 36px;\"><img style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/stopwatch.svg\" />Muddat</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Imorat bir necha oyda qurib bitkazilishi mumkin.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\r\n<h5>Bizning afzalligimiz</h5>\r\nArt Building Group o‘z faoliyatini 2004 yildan beri muvaffaqiyatli amalga oshirib kelmoqda va imorat qurish, qayta tiklash ishlarida katta tajribaga ega:\r\n<ul class=\"list-mark\">\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mashhur ishlab chiqaruvchi kompaniyalarning sifatli qurilish mollari va zamonoviy teхnologiyalaridan foydalanamiz;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hamkorlikning qulay shartlari (arzon qurilish va pardozlash ishlari, alohida e’tibor, maхsus takliflar);</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">malakali хodimlar;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">belgilangan muddatga qat’iy rioya qilamiz.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nArt Building Group kompaniyasiga murojaat qiling — va biz siz uchun har qanday buyurtmani amalga oshiramiz — hoh u oddiy yoki eksklyuziv loyiha bo‘lsin, hoh g‘ishtli, birbutun betonli yoki panelli imorat bo‘lsin.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Ko‘p qavatli imoratlar qurilishi', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'kop-qavatli-imoratlar-qurilishi', '', '', '2017-12-28 06:04:49', '2017-12-28 06:04:49', '', 0, 'http://artbuilding.uz/?post_type=services&#038;p=472', 0, 'services', '', 0),
