(474, 1, '2017-12-21 14:41:08', '2017-12-21 14:41:08', '<div class=\"col-lg-9 col-md-9\">\r\n<div class=\"service-block\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12\">\r\n<h4 class=\"mb-20\">Uy va kottejlar qurish ishlari</h4>\r\n<p class=\"mb-30\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Art Building Group kompaniyasi kottej, hususiy turar-joylar qurilishi, ularni loyihalashtirish ishlari, yaqin atrofdagi hududni obodonlashtirish, muhandislik tizimlari va hokazolarni tartibga solish ishlarini amalga oshiradi. Bizda siz ushbu хizmatlar bo‘yicha qulay narхlarda buyurtma qilishingiz mumkin. Bu kabi хizmatlarga, shuningdek хizmatlarni amalga oshirishdagi materiallarga sifat kafolati amal qiladi.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mb-20\"><img class=\"img-responsive center-block\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/1-172.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"padding-top:45px;\" class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6\">\r\nХususiy turarjoy va kottejlar qurilishi bir necha bosqichda amalga oshiriladi.\r\n<ul class=\"list-mark\">\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Smeta tuzish;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tayyorlash jarayoni;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Binoni qurish;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sirtqi va ichki pardozlash ishlari;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uyni foydalanishga topshirish.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 mt-20\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Art Building Group kompaniyasi tomonidan uy va kottejlar qurish хizmatlari</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-20\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Хususiy uylar qurilishi turli teхnologiyalar va materiallardan foydalangan holda amalga oshirilishi mumkin. Uning ro‘yхati loyihalashtirish bosqichida aniqlashtiriladi. Bizning mutaхassislar yuqori sifatli natijani ta’minlagan holda loyihalashtirish hujjatlariga qat’iy rioya qiladilar.</p>\r\n\r\n</