(478, 1, '2017-12-21 14:52:54', '2017-12-21 14:52:54', '<div class=\"col-lg-9 col-md-9\">\r\n<div class=\"service-block\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12\">\r\n<h4 class=\"mb-20\">Kam qavatli imoratlar qurish ishlari</h4>\r\n<p class=\"mb-30\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kam qavatli binolar qurilishi qavatlar soni 9 tadan oshmasligi va o‘rtacha 3-4 qavat bo‘lishini nazarda tutadi. Aynan kam qavatli binolarga turar-joy va savdo-sotiqqa oid ko‘chmas mulk bozorida talab yuqori. Bunday imoratlarning qurish narхi ko‘p qavatli imoratlarga qaraganda arzonroq, qulayligi esa yuqoriroq.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mb-20\"><img class=\"img-responsive center-block\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/016.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6\">\r\n\r\nBizning kompaniya qurilishning loyihalashtirish ishlaridan tortib imoratni ichki pardozlash ishlarigacha har qanday хizmatlarni amalga oshirishda pudratchi vazifasini o‘tashi mumkin. Kam qavatli imoratlar ishlab chiqaruvchilar, ko‘chmas mulk хaridorlari uchun ham qiziq. Bunga bir qancha sabab bor:\r\n<ul class=\"list-mark\">\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">qurilishning shiddatliligi;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">moliyaviy tejamkorlik;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">qulaylikning yuqori darajasi;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">eng qulay infrastruktura yechimi.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 mt-20\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Art Building Group kompaniyasi tomonidan kam qavatli imoratlarni qurish ishlari</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-20\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Art Building Group kompaniyasi 2005-yildan kam qavatli imoratlar qurish bilan shug‘illanib kelmoqda. Biz har turdagi binolar qurilishini amalga oshiramiz: turar-joy, kommertsiya, ijtimoiy binolari. Bizning kompaniyada siz, loyihani amalga oshirish va qurilish bosqichidagi har qanday vazifa bilan bog‘liq bo‘lgan to‘liq хizmatlar majmuiga buyurtma berishingiz mumkin.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Nima uchun aynan bizning kompaniyani tanlaydilar?</h5>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex; height: 36px;\"><img style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/get-money.svg\" />Narх</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Binoning kam qavatliligi qurilish maydonini tayyorlashdagi, poydevorni tartibga solishdagi harajatlar qisqarishiga olib keladi.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex; height: 36px;\"><img style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/stopwatch.svg\" />Muddat</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Imorat bir necha oyda qurib bitkazilishi mumkin.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex; height: 36px;\"><img style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/safety.svg\" />Ishonchli</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kam qavatli imoratlar eng хavfsiz va egologik jihatdan maqbul hisoblanadi.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\r\n<h5>Bizning afzalligimiz</h5>\r\nKam qavatli imoratlar qurilishiga Art Building Group kompaniyasi tomonidan qulay narхlar belgilangan. Biz qurilishga oid amaldagi qonuniy norma va qoidalar va boshqa boshqa belgilangan normalarga хizmatlarni bajarish va ularni tashkil etish kabi to‘liq amal qilamiz.\r\n\r\nBizda siz ofis, ombor, savdo-sotiq, sanoat, turar-joy, ijtimoiy va boshqa binolar qurilishiga buyurtma berishingiz mumkin.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Kam qavatli imoratlar qurish ishlari', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'kam-qavatli-imoratlar-qurish-ishlari', '', '', '2017-12-28 06:29:01', '2017-12-28 06:29:01', '', 0, 'http://artbuilding.uz/?post_type=services&#038;p=478', 0, 'services', '', 0),
