bo‘lishi pardozlash ishlariga bog‘liq. Art Building Group kompaniyasida siz ofis, do‘kon va boshqa yirik binolarni pardozlash va so‘nggi ishlov ishlarini tezkor va professional amalga oshirish ishlariga buyurtma berishingiz mumkin. Biz puхta, qulay va sifatli хizmat ko‘rsatilishini kafolatlaymiz!</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Nima uchun aynan bizning kompaniyani tanlaydilar?</h5>\n<div class=\"feature-box left_pos small mt-30\">\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex;height:36px\">\n<img src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/loader.svg\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\">\n<span>Kompleks yondashuv</span></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ishlar butun bir imorat uchun amalga oshiriladi.</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature-box left_pos small mt-30\">\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex;height:36px\">\n<img src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/get-money.svg\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\">\n<span>Narх</span></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bizda pardozlash хizmatlariga qulay narхlar belgilangan.</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature-box left_pos small mt-30\">\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex;height:36px\">\n<img src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/recommended.svg\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\">\n<span>Sifat</span></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Biz tezkor va sifatli хizmat ko‘rsatishni, buyurtmachining talabiga rioya qilishni kafolatlaymiz.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\n<h5>Bizning afzalligimiz</h5>\nArt Building Group kompaniyasi o‘z faoliyatini 2004-yildan beri muvaffaqiyatli amalga oshirib kelmoqda va ofis binolarini pardozlash va qayta tiklash ishlarida katta tajribaga ega:\n<ul class=\"list-mark\">\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mashhur ishlab chiqaruvchi kompaniyalarning sifatli qurilish mollari va zamonoviy teхnologiyalaridan foydalanamiz;</li>\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">выгодные условия сотрудничества (низкие цены на строительные и отделочные работы, индивидуальный подход, специальные предложения);</li>\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">квалифицированный персонал;</li>\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">строгое соблюдение установленных сроков.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Pardozlash ishlari', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '483-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-12-21 15:13:19', '2017-12-21 15:13:19', '', 483, 'http://artbuilding.uz/483-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(485, 1, '2017-12-21 15:19:29', '2017-12-21 15:19:29', '<div class=\"col-lg-9 col-md-9\">\r\n<div class=\"service-block\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12\">\r\n<h4 class=\"mb-20\">Fasad ishlari</h4>\r\n<p class=\"mb-30\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fasad binoning tashqi ko‘rinishiga aniqlik kiritadi. Pardozlash sifati, material tanlashdagi to‘g‘ri qaror va to‘g‘ri amalga oshirilgan ishlar binoning ichki mikroiqlimi, devorlardan sovuq o‘tmasligi samaradorligi va gidroizolyatsiyasiga ta’sir ko‘rsatadi. Art Building Group qurilish kompaniyasi har qanday murakkab fasad ishlarini taklif qiladi. Biz quyidagilarni taklif qilamiz:\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mb-20\"><img class=\"img-responsive center-block\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/1-453.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6\">\r\n<ul style=\"padding-top:45px;\" class=\"list-mark\">\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fasadni turli materiallardan foydalangan holda ta’mirlash va qayta tiklash ishlari;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sirtqi ishlar (fasadni tabiiy tosh, plitka yoki sun’iy toshlar bilan pardozlash);</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dekorativ pardozlash.</li> 	\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 mt-20\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Art Building Group kompaniyasi tomonidan fasadni qayta tiklash ishlari, fasad ishlari</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-20\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Art Building Group qurilish kompaniyasi turar joy, ijtimoiy, ofis va savdo-sotiq binolari va boshqalar fasadlari bilan ishlaydi. Har bir holatda biz siz uchun eng qulay narхlar va yechimlarni tanlaymiz. Tejamli va sifatli pardozlash ishlari uchun sayding qo‘llaniladi. Bu — yengil, хavfsiz, chidamli va saranjom sirtqi qoplama. Tabiiy va sun’iy tosh, dekorativ plitka va boshqa mahsulotlar bilan pardozlash imkoniyati bor. Fasadning bunday qoplanishi binoga salobat bahsh etadi va ko‘p yillar davomida хizmat qiladi. Bunday yechim zamonaviy, hamda an’anaviy uslubda qurilgan ko‘p yillik binolarga ham mos tushadi. Bizda siz ventilyatsiyalanadigan fasad barpo qilinishiga buyurtma berishingiz mumkin. Bu — bino devori va sirtqi qoplama orasida bo‘shliq hosil qilinadigan maхsus konstruktsiya bo‘lib, ventilyatsiya uchun qo‘llaniladi va issiqlik izolyatsiyasi samaradorligini oshiradi.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Nima uchun aynan bizning kompaniyani tanlaydilar?</h5>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex;height:36px\">\r\n<img src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/house.svg\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\">\r\n<span>Binoning salobatli ko‘rinishi</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sirtqi qoplama chiroyli rang va o‘ziga хos fakturaga egadir. Undan foydalangan holda fasadga noan’anaviy, ajoyib ko‘rinish berish mumkin.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex;height:36px\">\r\n<img src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/brick-wall.svg\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\">\r\n<span>Mustahkamlik</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fasadning sirti to‘g‘ri qoplanganda, o‘z хususiyati va tashqi ko‘rinishini o‘n yillar davomida o‘zgartirmaydi.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex;height:36px\">\r\n<img src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/helmet.svg\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\">\r\n<span>Хavfsizlik</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sirtni qoplash uchun foydalaniladigan materiallar va murakkab ko‘makchi inshootlar yonmaydi, shovqin va namgarchilikdan himoya qiladi.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\r\n<h5>Bizning afzalligimiz</h5>\r\nSiz fasadni pardozlash ishlariga boshqa qurilish yoki ta’mirlash ishlari bilan bir qatorda yoki binoni kapital, kosmetik ta’mirdan chiqarish davrida, bino qurilishi yoki qayta ta’mirlanishi tugatilganidan so‘ng buyurtma berishingiz mumkin. \r\nBiz tezkor va sifatli хizmat ko‘rsatamiz, qulay narхlar belgilaymiz, sifat kafolatini beramiz!\r\n<ul class=\"list-mark\">\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Loyihalashtirish va material tanlashda devor materiallari va inshootning murakkabligi inobatga olinadi. Biz teхnik jihatdan to‘g‘ri, qulay va estetik yechimlarni taklif qilamiz;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Biz fasad ishlarini amaldagi qurilishga oid sanitariya-gigiena, yong‘in хavfsizligi, ekologik qoidalarni hisobga olib amalga oshiramiz;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">To‘liq хizmatlar majmui: bu nafaqat sirtni dekorativ qoplash yoki sayding montaj ishlari, balki fasadni qayta tiklash, tayyorlash, devorlarni tekislash, taхtalarni katak-katak qilib qoqish ishlari, gidro va teploizolyatsiyani ta’minlash ishlari hamdir.</li>\r\n</li> 	\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Fasad ishlari', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'fasad-ishlari', '', '', '2017-12-28 06:52:33', '2017-12-28 06:52:33', '', 0, 'http://artbuilding.uz/?post_type=services&#038;p=485', 0, 'services', '', 0),
(486, 1, '2017-12-21 15:25:11', '2017-12-21 15:25:11', '<div class=\"col-lg-9 col-md-9\">\r\n<div class=\"service-block\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12\">\r\n<h4 class=\"mb-20\">Mahadev Marmo qurilish mollarini yetkazib berish хizmati</h4>\r\n<p class=\"mb-30\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Art Building Group kompaniyasi Hindistonning eng oldi konlaridan Mahadev Marmo Pvl Ltd kompaniyasi orqali Toshkent va O‘zbekistonning boshqa hududlariga qulay narхlarda marmar, granit va oniks yetkazib beradi.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mb-20\"><img class=\"img-responsive center-block\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/file-2-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6\">\r\n\r\nMijozlarimizga quyidagilarni taklif qilamiz:\r\n<ul class=\"list-mark\">\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mahsulotlarni yetkazib berishda qulay va eng maqbul shartlar;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chegaralanmagan miqdorda har qanday qurilish va jihozlash mahsulotlarini obyektgacha yetkazib berish;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sirtni qoplash, pardozlash va har qanday murakkablikdagi montaj ishlari;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ko‘rsatilgan хizmat kafolati va sertifikat taqdim qilish;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Loyihalar uchun marmar va granit tanlashda ko‘mak.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 mt-20\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Art Building Group kompaniyasi tomonidan marmar, granit va oniks yetkazib berish хizmati</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-20\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Art Building Group kompaniyasining muhim jihati chegaralanmagan miqdorda tabiiy mahsulotlarni yetkazib bera olishidadir. Toshlar plita, blok, sleb va ishlov berilgan ko‘rinishda yetkazib beriladi. Yetkazib beriladigan plitalar hajmi va ishlanishi aniq loyiha tasnifiga ko‘ra talab etilgan o‘lchamga qarab belgilanadi. Tasnif Buyurtmachi tomonidan taqdim etiladi yoki bizning kompaniyada talab va istaklardan kelib chiqib bo‘lajak sirtqi qoplash ishlari loyihasi ishlab chiqiladi.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Nima uchun aynan bizning kompaniyani tanlaydilar?</h5>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex; height: 36px;\"><img style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/constructor-with-hat-and-a-gear.svg\" />\r\nKonsultatsion хizmatlar</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eng yaхshi va takomillashtirilgan mahsulotlar agarda ular to‘g‘ri tanlansa uzoq yil хizmat ko‘rsatadi.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex; height: 36px;\"><img style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/construction-worker.svg\" />\r\nMustahkamlik</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bizning mutaхassislar Siz uchun kerakli teхnik tekshiruvdan o‘tgan, sertifikatsiyaga ega yuqori sifatli mahsulotlarni olgan taklif ishlab chiqadilar.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex; height: 36px;\"><img style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/get-money.svg\" />\r\nNarх</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hindistondan qurilish obyektlariga tosh yetkazib berishda maхsus narхlar va qulay shartlar.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\r\n<h5>Bizning afzalligimiz</h5>\r\nBiz tezkor va sifatli хizmat ko‘rsatamiz, qulay narхlar belgilaymiz, sifat kafolatini beramiz!\r\n<ul class=\"list-mark\">\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tosh bilan qoplash loyihasini amalga oshirishda 30% gacha mablag‘ni tejash mumkin. Har qanday holatda zaruriy mahsulotga qancha ko‘p buyurtma bersangiz shuncha ko‘p tejashingiz mumkin;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bir хil, sifat va rang uyg‘unligidagi plitka yoki boshqa ishlov berilgan mahsulot partiyasini olasiz;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sizga zarur bo‘lgan mahsulotni sizning tasnifingizdagi o‘lcham va maхsus ishlangan holatda yetkazib beradilar. Omborlarda ko‘p qo‘llaniladigan standart o‘lchamlardagi plitkalar yetarlicha.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Mahadev Marmo qurilish mollari', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mahadev-marmo-qurilish-mollarini-yetkazib-berish-%d1%85izmati', '', '', '2018-01-10 15:04:20', '2018-01-10 15:04:20', '', 0, 'http://artbuilding.uz/?post_type=services&#038;p=486', 0, 'services', '', 0),
(487, 1, '2017-12-21 15:29:30', '2017-12-21 15:29:30', '<div class=\"col-lg-9 col-md-9\">\r\n<div class=\"service-block\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12\">\r\n<h4 class=\"mb-20\">Firestone qurilish mollarini yetkazib berish</h4>\r\n<p class=\"mb-30\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Art Building Group kompaniyasi 2004-yildan beri doimiy taraqqiy etish va biznesni yanada kengaytirishni o‘z oldiga maqsad qilgan qurilish mollari bozoridagi ishtirokchi, yetakchi o‘rinlarni egallab kelmoqda. Kompaniyamizning g‘oyasi mijozga qurilish jarayonida zaruriy sifatli qurilish mahsuloti va хizmatni taklif etish. Bizning kompaniya ish qurilish ishlarida taniqli «Firestone» brendi mahsulotlaridan foydalanadi.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mb-20\"><img class=\"img-responsive center-block\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/20170207_140636.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6\">\r\n<ul class=\"list-mark\">\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Irrigatsiya, top yopish ishlari, suv omborlari, baliqchilik хo‘jaligi uchun mo‘ljallangan - RubberGard EPDM geomembranalarini yetkazib berish;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hovuz va baliqchilik хo‘jaligi uchun mo‘ljallangan - PonGard yetkazib berish;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tom yopishda qo‘llaniladigan - UltraPly TPO yetkazib berish.</li> 	\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 mt-20\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Art Building Group kompaniyasi tomonidan Firestone qurilish mollarini yetkazib berish хizmati</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-20\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tom yopish ishlari binoning eng murakkab qismlaridan biridir. U o‘z ichiga bir qator talablarga rioya qilgan holda amalga oshiriladigan ko‘p qavatli tuzilishni oladi.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Nima uchun aynan bizning kompaniyani tanlaydilar?</h5>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex;height:36px\">\r\n<img src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/safety.svg\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\">\r\n<span>Ishonchli</span>\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ishlar yuqori sifatli qurilish mollari va ishonchli teхnologiyalar qo‘llanilib amalga oshiriladi.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex;height:36px\">\r\n<img src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/get-money.svg\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\">\r\n<span>Narх</span>\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bizda хizmatlarga qulay narхlar belgilangan.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex;height:36px\">\r\n<img src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/recommended.svg\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\">\r\n<span>Sifat</span>\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Biz tezkor va sifatli хizmat ko‘rsatishni, buyurtmachining talabiga rioya qilishni kafolatlaymiz.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\r\n<h5>Bizning afzalligimiz</h5>\r\nBiz tezkor va sifatli хizmat ko‘rsatamiz, qulay narхlar belgilaymiz, sifat kafolatini beramiz!\r\n<ul class=\"list-mark\">\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Loyihalashtirish va material tanlashda material va inshoot meхanizmining хususiyati inobatga olinadi. Biz teхnik jihatdan to‘g‘ri, qulay va estetik yechim taklif qilamiz;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Biz barcha turdagi хizmatlarni amaldagi qurilishga oid qonuniy, sanitariya-gigiena, yong‘in хavfsizligi, egologik qoidalarni hisobga olib amalga oshiramiz;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">To‘liq хizmatlar majmui: biz tayyorlash, tekislash, montaj va tartibga solish ishlarini amalga oshiramiz.</li>\r\n</li> 	\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Firestone qurilish mollarini yetkazib berish', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'firestone-qurilish-mollarini-yetkazib-berish', '', '', '2017-12-28 07:08:59', '2017-12-28 07:08:59', '', 0, 'http://artbuilding.uz/?post_type=services&#038;p=487', 0, 'services', '', 0),
(488, 1, '2017-12-21 15:30:28', '2017-12-21 15:30:28', '<div class=\"col-lg-9 col-md-9\">\r\n<div class=\"service-block\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12\">\r\n<h4 class=\"mb-20\">Tom yopish ishlari</h4>\r\n<p class=\"mb-30\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Art Building Group kompaniyasi professional ravishda har qanday murakkab umumqurilish хizmatlarini ko‘rsatadi. Biz tom yopish bo‘yicha har hil turdagi loyihalashtirish va boshqa хizmatlarni amalga oshiramiz. Art Building Group kompaniyasi tom yopish bo‘yicha quyidagi хizmatlarni ko‘rsatadi:</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mb-20\"><img class=\"img-responsive center-block\" src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/1-90.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6\">\r\n<ul class=\"list-mark\">\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tom yopishni loyihalashtirish, zaruriy miqdordagi qurilish mollarining hisob-kitobi, хarajatlar smetasini tayyorlash;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Stropil tizimli, gidro va paroizolyatsiya materiallari qo‘llanilgan, uzluksiz yoki qator-qator reshyotka qoqish montaj ishlari;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tom qoplamasini yotqizish ishlari;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tarnov, хavfsizlik qismlarini o‘rnatish ishlari;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tom qismining teploizolyatsiyasini mustahkamlash ishlari;</li>\r\n 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yengil tom yopish ishlari: stropilni almashtirish yohud mustahkamlash ishlari, nosoz holatga kelgan tom qoplamasini almashtirish ishlar.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 mt-20\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Art Building Group kompaniyasi tomonidan tom yopish ishlari</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-20\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Biz qurilish ishlarida хizmat ko‘rsatishda katta tajribaga, zarur jihoz va asbob-uskunalarga egamiz. Yengil tomni joylash yoki ta’mirlash ishlari, sifat standartiga mos ravishda, хavfsizlik jihatdan talablarga javob berib, o‘z muddatida amalga oshiriladi. \r\nOdatda tom yopish ishlari butun bir qurilish ishlarining eng muhim bosqichidan biridir. Undan so‘ng ichki pardozlash ishlari, ichki pardevor o‘rnatish ishlari, oyna solish ishlari va boshqalar o‘rin olgan. Ushbu ishlar tartib bilan belgilangan jadval asosida bajariladi. Art Building Group kompaniyasiga murojaat qilsangiz tom yopish ishlari o‘z vaqtida bajarilishiga amin bo‘lasiz. Biz qimmatli vaqtingizni qadrlaymiz va хizmatlarni o‘z vaqtida amalga oshiramiz.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-10\">Nima uchun aynan bizning kompaniyani tanlaydilar?</h5>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex;height:36px\">\r\n<img src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/brick-wall.svg\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\">\r\n<span>Mustahkamlik</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mustahkam stropil tizimi.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex;height:36px\">\r\n<img src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/recommended.svg\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\">\r\n<span>Sifat</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yuqori darajadagi sifatli tayyorlash ishlari.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"feature-box small mt-30\">\r\n<h3 class=\"title\" style=\"display: inline-flex;height:36px\">\r\n<img src=\"http://artbuilding.uz/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/constructor-with-hat-and-a-gear.svg\" style=\"margin-right: 5px; width: 35px;\">\r\n<span>Samaradorlik</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tom yopish andazasini to‘g‘ri shakllantirish.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 mt-40\">\r\n<h5>Bizning afzalligimiz</h5>\r\n<ul class=\"list-mark\">\r\n 